Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.84,0:00:14.85,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Did you know that whenever a star shoots by, it signifies that one of their lives has ended?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.21,0:00:20.91,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,A contractor just died somewhere in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.56,0:00:30.79,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,The starry sky disappeared and was replaced with an imitation ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.65,0:00:34.50,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Cold-blooded, supernatural beings known as contractors...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.20,0:00:37.79,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Soulless physical entities called Dolls...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.58,0:00:42.34,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Various governments, who feared that information about contractors and Dolls would become widespread,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:49.72,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,utilized new, gate-derived technology called M.E. to erase the memories of those who came into contact with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.81,0:00:55.21,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Those very countries were taking advantage of their newfound abilities at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.37,0:00:57.74,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,You know a lot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.77,0:01:01.53,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,I've been working at a research lab for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.53,0:01:04.43,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,I learned things I shouldn't have known, whether I wanted to or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.03,0:01:08.54,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Besides, it seems we're destined to be acquainted for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.94,0:01:13.10,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,I think it was during high school when my parents died in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.83,0:01:17.61,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Well, that's what I was told. The truth was a little different.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.01,0:01:23.04,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,I witnessed it... The sight of a contractor killing my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.16,0:01:26.45,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,I think I became fascinated by them...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.37,0:01:28.79,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,ever since that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.43,0:01:37.68,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,The Division of Astronomy simultaneously confirmed French agent activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.68,0:01:41.99,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,His name is Jean, and he has the ability to perform a material exchange type of teleportation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.38,0:01:48.52,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Although the crime scene was identified through an observer apparition search, no clues were found.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.52,0:01:52.42,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,My sincere apologies. I missed a great opportunity to apprehend him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.19,0:01:59.51,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Although taking occasional breaks is important, dropping your guard could prove to be fatal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:03.33,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,There are signs of activity from that BK201 we're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.33,0:02:04.18,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:04.64,DTB-Default,Saitou&Kouno,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.88,0:02:11.28,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,This is all your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.28,0:02:13.02,DTB-Default,Kouno,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:14.90,Location,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\be1\fs45\c&H2B261E&\an4\frz15.842\fscx81.25\fscy92.5\frx4\fry356\fax-0.35\b0\pos(513,324)}Umitsuki Apartments
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:29.41,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,I see... So they're already on to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:35.32,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,You should change quickly. I'll be in my room next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:36.45,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,If there's anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.58,0:02:40.82,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,So it's true... What took place today...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.62,0:02:45.18,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Louis is a contractor, and he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.87,0:02:47.90,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.83,0:02:51.38,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Don't leave me by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:02:59.95,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Don't turn on the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:06.09,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,How strange... I should be used to the layout of the rooms,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.09,0:03:08.82,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,but seeing the other symmetrical half is a little weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:10.87,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,It's almost as if it's fake...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:15.64,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,It's only been two weeks since I moved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:19.51,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,During that time, I actually felt as if I was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:22.22,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,It was the first time I felt that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.62,0:03:26.55,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,I thought it would be impossible for me to work at a club.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:29.06,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Once I tried it, it became surprisingly addicting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:34.60,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,One part of me was constantly mired in research, as if it were possessed. The other part was as I am right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:42.32,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell what my real personality was. I was even more confused because Louis was coming to pick me up soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.98,0:03:44.37,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,which made me feel overjoyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:48.95,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,It looks like I can't go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:52.29,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Do you have any plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:55.94,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:57.92,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Louis was my only hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:02.77,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I'll help you out somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.48,0:04:04.20,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:07.14,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Let's run away together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:14.09,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,But... But you just moved in today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:17.65,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I was probably destined to come here today
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.12,0:04:19.90,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,and meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:22.95,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,It said so on my horoscope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:33.51,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,What are you saying? You're more than capable of running away by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.51,0:04:34.76,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Forget about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.76,0:04:36.91,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,They saw my face, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:39.21,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Sooner or later, this room will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:44.44,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Can I... trust you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.63,0:05:04.14,DTB-Default,Kouno,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:05.78,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,Someone beat us to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:08.62,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,In any case, let's search for clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:10.49,DTB-Default,Kouno,0,0,0,,Think something will turn up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:24.22,DTB-Default,Kouno,0,0,0,,A cat, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:32.81,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,There's an acquaintance of mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:37.78,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,He conducts trading-related business in Macau.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:41.68,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,He can provide passports and the like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.68,0:05:45.09,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Counterfeit? You mean like forging documents for illegal residency?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:52.74,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,You told me you were an exchange student, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:56.29,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I have my own set of circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:06:01.79,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,When did this country become so dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:05.22,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,However, lots of money will be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:06.98,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Money, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.44,0:06:10.50,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,I should have withdrawn more from the bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:13.56,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,If you have something that's worth money...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:16.57,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,How about information?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.57,0:06:17.92,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Information?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:23.98,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Like confidential information obtained by illegally accessing Pandora's central system.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:25.82,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:29.42,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Gate-related information usually sells at a high price,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:31.43,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,no matter how insignificant it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.43,0:06:37.09,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,It's the most revolutionary theory since those on compressed gravitational repulsive elements and the M.E. technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:40.53,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,It'll definitely sell for a high price.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:43.59,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Haraguchi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:49.96,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Haraguchi is a pseudonym. My actual name is Chiaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.96,0:06:52.05,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Shinoda Chiaki, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:56.20,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Chiaki-san... That's a nice name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:57.89,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Pleased to make your acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:07:00.10,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,My name is Li Shun Sheng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:02.20,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Li-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:04.52,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,That's a good name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:07.74,DTB-Default,Waitress,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:12.46,DTB-Default,Waitress,0,0,0,,Is this everything you ordered?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.46,0:07:13.37,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:14.85,DTB-Default,Waitress,0,0,0,,Enjoy your meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.43,0:07:21.87,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,I did say you could order anything you wanted, but are you really going to eat everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:26.75,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. This is less than what I usually eat, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:33.36,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Listen, you're going to get fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.36,0:07:34.60,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,For sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:38.93,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,It might be okay for you now, but after you turn thirty, you're definitely going to become obese.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:41.01,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,If that doesn't happen, there's something wrong with the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:49.94,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Then again, who am I to be worrying about the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:10.17,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:16.43,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,I've been feeling a little tired lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:19.43,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Go ahead and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:36.32,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I see. Although I've already heard about it, I'm impressed with how you conduct yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:38.37,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Huang...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:42.49,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,There isn't a better fit for these kinds of jobs than your kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.43,0:08:46.77,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,After all, you don't have the slightest sense of guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.91,0:08:52.62,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,You have an idea about where the goods are, right? Hurry up and acquire it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:56.94,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,They're already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.94,0:08:59.92,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Trash the woman before she becomes a hinderance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:03.34,DTB-Default,Waitress,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:28.00,DTB-Default,Waitress,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:29.42,DTB-Default,Waitress,0,0,0,,Party of two?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:35.84,DTB-Default,Waitress,0,0,0,,Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:40.00,DTB-Default,Cook A,0,0,0,,Hey, you can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:41.63,DTB-Default,Cook B,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:03.62,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:04.88,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:05.83,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:22.25,DTB-Default,Alain,0,0,0,,Jean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:24.99,DTB-Default,Alain,0,0,0,,They escaped. Let's reconvene.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:27.77,DTB-Default,Alain,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's the mouse, there's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:40.68,Title,,0,0,0,,Episode Two The Fallen Star of a Contract... (Part Two)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.65,0:10:45.29,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,He's been offline.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:48.79,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,What's going on? Don't tell me he's going to double-cross us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:52.74,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,He has nothing to gain by betraying us in this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.74,0:10:56.25,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Contractors don't act unless they benefit from doing so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:58.28,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Well, he's acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:11:00.84,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Why didn't he waste the broad already?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:02.68,DTB-Default,Hunag,0,0,0,,He's taking too much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:05.29,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,I must admit he's pretty unconventional.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:07.09,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,What is Hei doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.09,0:11:07.89,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:08.56,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:11.34,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,There's no water near him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.18,0:11:15.16,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:15.91,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:23.93,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. This is all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:29.04,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,It's impossible after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:31.61,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,We can't run away from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:35.58,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Your face looks tired,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:37.88,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,as if you were already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:40.14,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,You should rest now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:42.97,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,I am tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:46.81,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,I've had enough of this charade.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:54.43,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Every time I try to run away, they appear before I realize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.43,0:11:58.19,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Always intruding upon my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:11:59.61,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,I won't forgive them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:08.58,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,But even more unforgivable is that, despite everything, I keep watching them in the corner of my eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:11.92,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,What's wrong with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:14.00,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,But I realized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:20.38,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,That time... When my parents died, I saw everything but I didn't testify against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.97,0:12:23.86,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,The contractor was still a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:26.76,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Although I couldn't see the face...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:34.98,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,The glow of the Lancernopt synchrotron radiation I saw in the dark lingered in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:37.65,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,It was beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.72,0:12:43.44,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,It was my own life, yet it felt like I was watching someone else's dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:44.36,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.98,0:12:46.92,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,You would be better off without them...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:49.31,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,The memories of a contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:54.89,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,I couldn't bring myself to forget about these memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:58.14,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be the person I am today if I had forgotten them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:02.38,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,These feelings scare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:14.56,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,I'm sure you have your own memories you wish you were able to forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:24.99,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Contractors aren't people. They're killing machines beneath the guise of a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:27.23,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.23,0:13:32.44,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Witnesses are always eliminated in order to minimize risks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:36.44,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,They're liars and traitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:41.88,Location,,0,0,0,,{\be1\bord0\shad0\fs60\fnArial Black\b1\fscx90\c&H494949&\frx8\fry352\frz0.311\pos(618,357)\fax-0.03}Service suspended
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:03.69,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,How did they know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.44,0:14:28.57,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,You must forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:37.23,DTB-Default,Cop A,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:40.98,DTB-Default,Cop A,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:52.26,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,This is Saitou. A call came in from the Mita Precinct that stated they were taking Shinoda, the missing woman, into custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:55.37,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,The presumably French agents were also seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:56.84,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,I'm on the way to the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.84,0:14:59.71,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Affirmative. I'll call for assistance immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:04.35,DTB-Default,Mayu,0,0,0,,Activity from BK201 has been confirmed by the Division of Astronomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.35,0:15:05.19,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:08.49,DTB-Default,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,Boss, this is Matsumoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:10.88,DTB-Default,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,Shinoda Chiaki's corpse has been identified.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:12.89,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.36,0:15:19.56,DTB-Default,Cop B,0,0,0,,Can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:20.74,DTB-Default,Cop A,0,0,0,,Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:31.21,DTB-Default,Cop A,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:58.27,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,,Are you a contractor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:16:00.14,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,,So you're the one who killed Louis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.81,0:16:10.11,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,You... killed Louis?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:12.40,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.38,0:16:14.55,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,You're lying...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:18.24,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Didn't I already tell you? Contractors are liars.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:22.12,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,,The mouse was caught in the trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:33.94,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,,That woman isn't Shinoda Chiaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.94,0:16:39.64,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,,She's only a Doll with the memories of Shinoda Chiaki, extracted from her by the M.E.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:46.14,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,,By saying the keyword, she has been detached from her programmed personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:50.28,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,,In any case, her personality would only have lasted two or three more days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:55.03,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,,It was a trap in order to lure you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:02.71,DTB-Default,Alain,0,0,0,,To think he fell for it so easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:04.62,DTB-Default,Alain,0,0,0,,Was Louis really killed by this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:10.59,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Unfortunately for you, Hei's jacket provides a bulletproof effect while he's wearing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:12.31,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:21.13,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,,Alain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:51.20,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:05.72,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,As I thought, this one was a decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.42,0:18:10.20,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,The goods have been confiscated through another route.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:13.36,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,The syndicate predicted everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.50,0:18:17.20,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Why didn't you destroy that doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:21.97,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,She wasn't a Doll. She was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:26.02,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,It's just a doll, a passive medium.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:30.42,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Much like how you contractors are mere killing accessories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:33.52,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Enough, Huang. Our work isn't finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:35.42,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Yin, where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.21,0:18:37.84,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,I have a lead on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:42.41,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:45.63,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Excuse me. We're from the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:50.93,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I wanted to inquire about your neighbor, Haraguchi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.93,0:19:54.29,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Have you noticed anything peculiar about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:58.92,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I only recently moved in, so I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:01.06,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Are you from abroad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.06,0:20:05.68,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but may I see your alien registration card?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.11,0:20:07.92,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.78,0:20:12.29,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:16.35,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,If you remember anything about her, please contact me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:18.17,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I appreciate your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:28.33,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,Boss, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:31.74,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.91,0:20:35.44,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Let's go, Saitou.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:36.12,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.27,0:20:45.18,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Hell was supposed to be confined within the fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:50.28,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The blue light released by the petal is a memento of the forgotten past.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:54.43,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Stop it. She's not to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:21:00.36,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The scream becomes inaudible, and the illuminated star signifies the mark of a contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:04.39,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,A permanent curse that cannot be erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.39,0:21:07.38,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Eventually, the light will be extinguished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:09.49,Title,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Episode Three A New Star Shines in the Dawn Sky... (Part One)